WEBVTT

00:12.971 --> 00:14.806
<i>( knock on door )</i>

00:14.890 --> 00:16.558
Man:
<i>Coming.</i>

00:30.072 --> 00:32.533
‐ OK.
‐ Mr. Bracamonte?

00:32.616 --> 00:36.119
‐ Good. You got your printer.
‐ Yeah.

00:58.100 --> 00:59.601
I recognize you.

00:59.685 --> 01:02.354
From the bus ads.
The lawyer.

01:02.437 --> 01:05.148
I want you to change
my last will.

01:05.232 --> 01:07.109
The old one is there.

01:09.319 --> 01:11.446
Your... will?

01:12.781 --> 01:14.408
It won't be hard.

01:17.911 --> 01:19.746
Any notary can do it.

01:20.664 --> 01:22.332
<i>It's easy.</i>

01:32.593 --> 01:34.261
<i>( opens drawer )</i>

01:38.307 --> 01:39.725
<i>( closes drawer )</i>

01:39.808 --> 01:42.436
( sighs ) What's that?

01:47.816 --> 01:48.859
My medicine.

01:55.032 --> 01:56.742
I'll need a witness,

01:56.825 --> 01:59.661
and I'll also need
to film us doing this

01:59.745 --> 02:01.747
<i>so it'll stand in court.</i>

02:01.830 --> 02:03.624
My daughter
should be here soon.

02:03.707 --> 02:06.752
‐ <i>( knock on door )</i>
‐ And there she is.

02:06.835 --> 02:08.128
It's open.

02:27.522 --> 02:29.733
How long have you been
in here?

02:31.068 --> 02:33.987
I'm dying, Dolores.

02:38.742 --> 02:42.287
OK, the document
has been dictated
and proofread

02:42.371 --> 02:44.790
by Mr. Lalo Bracamonte.

02:44.873 --> 02:47.292
Do you swear
no one has coerced you

02:47.376 --> 02:50.003
in any way
in the creation of this?

02:50.087 --> 02:51.380
Lalo: <i>Mm‐hmm.</i>

02:54.800 --> 02:57.719
Do you, Dolores Bracamonte,

02:57.803 --> 03:01.348
<i>swear to have been witness</i>
<i>and in no way‐‐</i>

03:01.431 --> 03:04.226
I haven't done anything
and I won't sign anything.

03:04.309 --> 03:06.728
Lalo:
<i>She won't have to.</i>

03:11.024 --> 03:12.109
( mutters )

03:16.780 --> 03:18.448
( speaking Spanish )

03:18.532 --> 03:20.909
( speaking Spanish )

04:00.991 --> 04:02.451
OK, this is it.

04:02.534 --> 04:04.411
<i>I think this is it.</i>

04:06.663 --> 04:09.040
You will mail
those two copies tonight?

04:09.124 --> 04:10.917
Yes, Mr. Bracamonte.

04:11.001 --> 04:13.336
Leave my copy over there
with the other one.

04:23.555 --> 04:25.348
Um...

04:25.432 --> 04:27.350
You're not gonna
make any more money.

04:30.979 --> 04:34.191
This was a pretty
unusual request.

04:42.866 --> 04:44.117
Just go.

04:44.201 --> 04:46.870
I mean, i‐it's just‐‐

04:47.996 --> 04:49.331
( chokes )

04:58.006 --> 05:00.091
Lalo: <i>You know</i>
<i>how fucking miserable it is</i>

05:00.175 --> 05:01.343
<i>to deal with a shit like you</i>

05:01.426 --> 05:03.136
at a time like this?

05:04.095 --> 05:05.222
( speaking Spanish )

05:17.484 --> 05:18.985
( gasps )

05:24.616 --> 05:26.201
Goodbye.

